return function(self, player) if player.hitHaypatch then return end if player.walkingThroughHaypatch then if love.keyboard.isDown("up") or love.keyboard.isDown("down") or love.keyboard.isDown("left") or love.keyboard.isDown("right") then self.sprite:setAnimation("waffle") else self.sprite:setAnimation("idle") end return end
if not (GameState.leader == "sonic" and player.doingSpecialMove) then player.origMoveSpeed = player.movespeed player.movespeed = 1 player.walkingThroughHaypatch = true return end
